title: Clinton's email woes spin a tale about the ascendance of IT
text: Clinton's email woes spin a tale about the ascendance of IT Thursday, 10 September 2015 (12 minutes ago) The former State Department worker who set up Hillary Rodham Clinton's email server is scheduled to appear before House investigators behind closed doors on Thursday.
